          p Discover the latest trends in fashion with our exclusive collection at Trendy Treasures!
          
        .promo.text-center.shadow-sm
          img(src='https://cdn.vibecity.in/providers/6496f744617db20d8ee2748c/310e7544-4b9d-4fc2-9de2-fb076b340f31_105a2b0d-11df-4a30-b9f1-df5bc86b729f-4X.png', alt='Promotional Image 2', class='img-fluid')
          p Shop our curated selection of clothing and accessories that cater to all styles.

        .promo.text-center.shadow-sm
          img(src='https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/03/34/79/68/360_F_334796865_VVTjg49nbLgQPG6rgKDjVqSb5XUhBVsW.jpg', alt='Promotional Image 3', class='img-fluid')
